Microsoft's Innovation Hub provides world-class processes, resources and support for helping to drive, build and control innovation within customer organisations. The next big idea could come from anywhere within your company - the Innovation Hub ensures an easy and collaborative way to engage everyone.

Enable colleagues to collaborate and perform with connected applications as part of Office 365, available from desktop, browser and mobile devices.  Employees can be productive from anywhere and at any time, benefitting from video conferencing and instant messaging, intuitive and easy access to documents in the cloud, on-premise or a hybrid of both, and social tools to boost team effectiveness and output.
